y, and to cause disaster, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 21:10","book":"Jer","chapter":21,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 39:16","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 44:27","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":27,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 9:4","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" so will I watch over them to build and to plant them” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 1:10","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 18:7–10","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":7,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 44:27","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":27,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" —this is the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s declaration. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 21:10","book":"Jer","chapter":21,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 39:16","book":"Jer","chapter":39,"verse":16},{"label":"Jr 44:27","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":27},{"label":"Am 9:4","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":4},{"label":"Jr 1:10","book":"Jer","chapter":1,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 18:7–10","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 44:27","book":"Jer","chapter":44,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:31:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“In those days, it will never again be said,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:31:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Rather, each will die for his own iniquity. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 24:6","book":"Deu","chapter":24,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 18:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":18,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Anyone who eats sour grapes —his own teeth will be set on edge."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 24:6","book":"Deu","chapter":24,"verse":6},{"label":"Ezk 18:20","book":"Ezk","chapter":18,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305e