e coming” —the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s declaration —“when the city "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"= Jerusalem"},{"kind":"text","text":" from the Tower of Hananel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 3:1","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 12:39","book":"Neh","chapter":12,"verse":39,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the Corner Gate "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 14:13","book":"2Ki","chapter":14,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 26:9","book":"2Ch","chapter":26,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 14:10","book":"Zec","chapter":14,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" will be rebuilt for the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Neh 3:1","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Neh 12:39","book":"Neh","chapter":12,"verse":39},{"label":"2Kg 14:13","book":"2Ki","chapter":14,"verse":13},{"label":"2Ch 26:9","book":"2Ch","chapter":26,"verse":9},{"label":"Zch 14:10","book":"Zec","chapter":14,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"= Jerusalem"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:31:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A measuring line will once again stretch out straight to the hill of Gareb "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zch 2:1","book":"Zec","chapter":2,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and then turn toward Goah. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Zch 2:1","book":"Zec","chapter":2,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:31:40","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The whole valley —the corpses, the ashes, and all the fields as far as the Kidron Valley "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 23:4","book":"2Ki","chapter":23,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the corner of the Horse Gate "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 3:28","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":28,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":"